FINAL OBJECTIVE

====================================================

Generate a visually stunning, emotionally persuasive, conversion-focused hospitality website that makes visitors trust the property within 5 seconds, understand the location advantage within 15 seconds, and feel compelled to click BOOK NOW before leaving the homepage.

The experience should feel comparable to a premium international hospitality brand while remaining authentic to Membley, Ruiru, and the modern Kenyan traveler.
